{"tid":1048877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍李東海小學女教師校內墮樓亡　胞弟哭斥校長要求無理","createTime":"2019-03-06T01:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T10:52:08.000Z","uid":6497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25111e2f0f473851e450f48dcdcf253d873d9531","tid":1048877,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190306/s00001/262724c5d1edcfae061c303f5082da0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190306%2Fs00001%2F262724c5d1edcfae061c303f5082da0d.jpg&h=947a0b38&s={SIZE}\" />死者家人抱頭痛哭，斥校長經常對死者有無理要求。（蔡方山攝）<br />\n<br />\n早上7時許，天水圍東華三院李東海小學有一名女子從6樓高處墮下，昏迷倒臥地上，職員見狀報警。救護員到場證實女事主當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查。現場消息指，死者為該校一名42歲女教師，一名自稱死者胞弟的男子到場後，向記者哭訴涉事小學校長常有無理要求，令死者有工作壓力，其後再有兩名死者家屬到場，眼泛淚光異口同聲指死者經常訴說與校方管理層關係欠佳。3人其後跟隨警員進入校內了解。"},{"pid":"d93de2e15d24b375e7ba754ff1b673e2569e69f1","tid":1048877,"uid":139700,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:19:12.000Z","msg":"香港幾時爆真正嘅階級鬥爭"},{"pid":"16a3ddf176f589704dde9f7737a98dba1c63ff87","tid":1048877,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756b2a686fab2c39bb2a6c76294dc7ff5628539c","tid":1048877,"uid":69168,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"真係慘，7點我都未訓醒，<br />\n佢已經返咗工灰完跳埋樓"},{"pid":"4e3ed74500be3546010671e69a669741bf7452b2","tid":1048877,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16a3ddf176f589704dde9f7737a98dba1c63ff87","tid":1048877,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"乘機輸入支那教師一踏入校園就要操北話"},{"pid":"b6b1888c250450a37b3ebd572ebed1c8136eb6c2","tid":1048877,"uid":36494,"li